{"tid":970016,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"炒股最重要的性格是...","createTime":"2019-01-05T13:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T02:31:02.000Z","uid":76531,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b24d17a2354309b091c7371b019c03f9981e7386","tid":970016,"uid":76531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"炒股的人，每一次買賣都是當下的承擔，<br />\n所以適合的一個重要性格是堅韌性。<br />\n太剛容易冒進，太柔容易萎縮。<br />\n堅韌，既敢於承擔又能消融這種承擔的壓力。<br />\n敢於承擔是靠剛性，能消融壓力是靠柔性。<br />\n太癡迷於金錢的人，在市場波動面前易方寸大亂，失之於一個&ldquo;緊&rdquo;字。<br />\n過於淡泊的人，對市場缺乏熱情，失之於一個&ldquo;松&rdquo;字。<br />\n不松不緊、剛柔並濟是置身市場的完美品格。<br />\n在市場中，外求內化是永恒的主題。<br />\n外求是求知，內化是變化自身氣質。<br />\n度的把握沒有先驗的結論，<br />\n要在市場中不斷觀照自己的內心。"},{"pid":"6f7b5af3ffda325613f68670d68753d4f5c57816","tid":970016,"uid":198241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"咁深？？？？<br />\n難賭咪得law<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a11d4c980d14e9b67a534f09d6a03a723de4c4","tid":970016,"uid":36849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:44:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a6051fc4f9e29ae20a76151dceabbaa18dbde98","tid":970016,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"清楚明白"},{"pid":"675340ac4b217f28e08e5a3b76576657ac08f3d1","tid":970016,"uid":126042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a6051fc4f9e29ae20a76151dceabbaa18dbde98","tid":970016,"uid":82542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"清楚明白"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T18:10:54.000Z","msg":"股票 就係槓桿槓桿再槓桿<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7923a632ac4a7fa618a98ac03c0306edb424c0","tid":970016,"uid":212947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T18:16:17.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb65ab35328e32010ffc1169396715056dfee91","